          Knowly is provided for personal use to help you capture and organize
          your lessons and insights. You agree to use the app lawfully and
          responsibly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Your Content</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          You retain ownership of all content you create in Knowly. We do not
          claim any rights to your lessons, notes, or other content.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Disclaimer</h2>
