        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, we are not liable for any
          indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of
          Knowly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the app
          after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Questions about these terms? Contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@getknowlyapp.com" class="text-secondary hover:underline">support@getknowlyapp.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
